Boat Rentals
.entry-header
Make the most of your stay at
Presnell’s Bayside Marina & RV Resort
with our top-quality boat and kayak rentals. Whether you’re looking for a relaxing day on the bay, an exciting fishing adventure, or a scenic paddle along the coastline, we have the perfect rental for you. Enjoy easy access to St. Joseph Bay’s pristine waters, world-class fishing, and
unbeatable scalloping grounds
—all just steps from our marina.
